not keeping your head down like this.

266
00:19:36,740 --> 00:19:38,980
If you keep your head down,

267
00:19:38,980 --> 00:19:44,280
how can you see whether you should defend or fight back?

268
00:19:52,180 --> 00:19:55,880
Hey, are you going to cry?

269
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:58,400
No.

270
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:05,640
Be patient. Then your fear will disappear.

271
00:20:20,300 --> 00:20:22,960
A man's tears.

272
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:25,940
I'll practice wiping it for you for now.

273
00:20:25,940 --> 00:20:27,590
I won't comfort you the next time.

274
00:20:27,590 --> 00:20:32,160
You must learn to stand on your feet.

275
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:36,020
I haven't even cried yet.

276
00:20:36,020 --> 00:20:41,220
Stop being weak or whining in front of others.

277
00:20:41,220 --> 00:20:43,760
Five, Four, Three,

278
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:46,141
Two, One!

279
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:48,380
First round is a draw.

280
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:57,060
Come on! Let's get it!

281
00:20:57,060 --> 00:21:04,860
